MedicationRequestPatientGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter patient.given:string

Searches for MedicationRequest based on the patient's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/MedicationRequest?patient.given={givenName}

ResourceMedicationRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesMedicationRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
